xmlgTestGeneral.name: MscRegistration
xmlgTestGeneral.xmlgShortDescription: Initlialize and register H248 stack, simulating the MGW Server
xmlgTestGeneral.xmlgDetailedDescription: The enabling of H248Cfg usually causes the generation of a H.248 v2 ServiceChangeRequest towards MSC-S to register the profile and version currently used by MGW. Since the COMDB scripts upload is not integrated with Pegasus, there would be no MSC-S to receive such a message and to reply in the proper way. Hence the command of H248Cfg enabling is removed from the scripts and is included in this Test Suite, together with the handling of the resulted ServiceChange REQ and RSP messages.
